added.title: Apple's in Trouble
added.description: Apple is challenged to a fight by a grumpy Cheesesteak, so he and Onion go on a quest to find the source of Cheesesteak's grumpiness.

added.title: 4 on 1
added.description: Onion's fear of crowds threatens his basketball team's success.

added.title: Hotdog's Movie Premiere
added.description: Apple and Onion square off against a no-nonsense security guard after they're banned from the premiere of their friend Hot Dog's new movie.

added.title: Bottle Catch
added.description: Apple and Onion's favorite game attracts some unexpected attention.

added.title: Pancake's Bus Tour
added.description: Apple and Onion go on a guided bus tour as part of their plan to get Apple's shoe back.

added.title: Block Party
added.description: Apple and Onion have to outwit a mean duck who's taken over their building's roof.

added.title: The Date
added.description: When Chef is happy he orders pizza for the kids, this gives Owen & Jude the idea to create a fake secret admirer for Chef.

added.title: Aquarium for a Dream
added.description: Gwen tries to convince Chef to tell the class the truth about their pet goldfish.

added.title: Cuttin' Corners
added.description: Duncan, Leshawna and Jude all want corner pieces of Izzy's Birthday Cake… But are they prepared to go to any length to get one?

added.title: Sharing Is Caring
added.description: Courtney refuses to share her valuable collectors item toy with her classmates.

added.title: Ant We All Just Get Along
added.description: Owen and Beth try to save an ant hill that Courtney and Leshawna want to destroy.

added.title: Germ Factory
added.description: After seeing Leshawna enjoying a sick day at home with ice cream and TV, Duncan convinces the other kids try to get sick too.

added.title: Falls, Falls, Falls
added.description: Team Tennyson looks to take in the sights of the Shoshone Falls, but when they arrive to find Steam Smythe siphoning off the water, it is up to Ben to distract the steam punk baddie long enough to allow Grandpa Max and Gwen the time to shut down the hydropower plant and save the Falls.

added.title: The Greatest Lake
added.description: While visiting Lake Erie, a relaxing day at the beach gets all washed up when Ben, Gwen and Grandpa Max come face-to-face with Hex, and his summer intern, Kevin!

added.title: Mud on the Run
added.description: Ben gets a tough lesson on knowing his limits when he competes in a grueling obstacle race, made even worse by the Weatherheads!

added.title: It's Story Time
added.description: After the Rustbucket breaks down, Ben, Gwen and Grandpa Max find themselves killing time at the local town library but soon scramble to out maneuver Hex as he searches for a hidden ancient artifact.

added.title: Cosplay Day
added.description: Team Tennyson enjoy the biggest convention in town, but when a gawky costume store employee finds a familiar-looking helmet in the back of the store and tries it on, Ben is faced with the return of an old foe in a new form: Forever Knight!

added.title: Bottomless Ben
added.description: While visiting Carlsbad Caverns National Park, the Tennyson's come across the "Bottomless Pit", a naturally formed pit with no bottom. Ben fights his better judgment to jump in the pit and be the first person to find the bottom, until Kevin 11 shows up and starts to goad Ben into a contest to the bottom of the pit! The natural rivalry is put on hold, however, with the arrival of Breaker One-Nine, who has come to destroy the Caverns!

added.title: Tales from the Omnitrix
added.description: Team Tennyson trade campfire stories in an anthology-style series that pits Ben against his archrival, Kevin 11, and teaches our hero the power of imagination.

added.title: Queen of Bees
added.description: Ben, Gwen and Grandpa Max arrive in Bismarck, North Dakota for its annual celebration of bee pollination, bringing them face-to-face with Queen Bee and a bold new scheme, forcing Ben to conquer his new fear of bees!

added.title: Two Sides of the Coin/The Race for Gold
added.description: Two Sides of the Coin: The AO and Magnus take parallel tracks to retrieve the same piece of data, one that promises a breakthrough in the Bakugan phenomenon./The Race for Gold: When the AO seek out a mythical, lost Bakugan, they get more than they bargained for when Magnus is on the trail of this new discovery, too.

added.title: Seek and Hide/Family First
added.description: Seek and Hide: Sent to investigate a Japanese island by Benton Dusk, the AO discover a hidden facility conducting experiments that affect The Hide./Family First: Trapped by his father, Shun is forced to battle his own friends, revealing dark secrets about the Kazami family and Masato's experiments.

added.title: A Door Closes, A Door Opens/Kazami's Gambit
added.description: A Door Closes, A Door Opens: Shun must stand up to his father, expose his cousin and protect his friends before Masato destroys everyone on Ichiro's island!/Kazami's Gambit: When Magnus looks to steal the Dimensional Doorway, Shun and Ichiro must make peace while the AO stop the Doorway from destroying them all.

added.title: A Devil on Your Shoulder/Vestral Visions
added.description: A Devil on Your Shoulder: Near giving up, Magnus gains new strength and insight on the AO's mission to find Core Cells that will eventually lead him down a dark hole./Vestral Visions: Drago's sickness leads Dan to a revelation that there is an ailing Core Cell and if they can't find a cure, the planet itself may falter.

added.title: Bakuzoned!/The Golden Secret
added.description: Bakuzoned!: Strata's return is much more than a simple rematch when he's been infected by a strange ooze and the AO are in danger of the same fate./The Golden Secret: Using Strata's gauntlet, the AO think they've found a way through the labyrinth, but soon discover trusting the enemy is not always best.

added.title: The Bakugan Breakers/The Awful Ones
added.description: The Bakugan Breakers: Magnus's new team of Bakugan Brawlers overhear Lightning's warnings of a sick Core Cell and decide to capture the dog to find its location./The Awful Ones: Magnus heads into the Labyrinth to claim the Fortus Core Cell for his own, but comes in direct contact with the evil versions of the AO.

added.title: Conquistando torres
added.description: Duncan, Leshawna y Jude quieren una pieza de esquina del pastel de cumpleaños de Izzy, pero, ¿están preparados para hacer cualquier cosa por conseguir uno?

added.title: Atrapa la Botella
added.description: Manzana y Cebollín inventan un nuevo juego que atrae una atención inesperada.

added.title: Compartir es querer
added.description: Courtney se niega a compartir su valioso juguete de coleccionista con sus amigos.

added.title: El Paseo en Autobus de Pancake
added.description: Manzana y Cebollín suben a un autobús que da un tour guiado como parte de su plan para recuperar el zapato de Manzana.

added.title: Y todos nos llevamos bien
added.description: Owen y Beth tratan de salvar un hormiguero que Courtney y Leshawna quieren destruir.

added.title: Fiesta en la Cuadra
added.description: Manzana y Cebollín deben ser más astutos que un pato malvado que se apoderó del techo de su edificio.

added.title: Chile libre
added.description: Cuando Owen oculta un walkie talky dentro de su perro con chile, Harold cree que es un alienígena que vino a destruir la tierra.

added.title: Manzana esta en Problemas
added.description: Bistec con Queso, malhumorado, desafía a Manzana a una pelea. De ese modo, Manzana puede embarcarse con Cebollín en una misión para encontrar el origen del malhumor de Bistec con Queso.

added.title: 4 a 1
added.description: El temor de Cebollín a las multitudes amenaza el éxito de su equipo de baloncesto.

added.title: La pecera de los suenos
added.description: Gwen trata de convencer a Chef de que le diga a la clase la verdad sobre su pececito dorado.

added.title: Hot Dog estrena su pelicula
added.description: Cuando unos guardias de seguridad muy serios los echan del estreno de la nueva película de su amigo Hot Dog, Manzana y Cebollín se preparan para pelear.

added.title: Fabrica de germenes
added.description: Después de ver a Leshawna disfrutar de un día enferma en casa con helado y TV, Duncan convence a los otros chicos de que traten de enfermarse.
